 Demonstrators including Game of Thrones actor Jason Momoa demanded the state and University of Hawaii stop construction of a new $ 1.4 billion telescope on sacred land .
Dozens of protesters were arrested on Thursday at the Mauna Kea site , a mountain burial ground said to be visited by the snow goddess Poli'u and a Native Hawaiian leader has called for a 30-day moratorium on construction .
The Thirty Meter Telescope will be one of the largest space observation facilities in the world .